項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1527%2c20211028%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,簡,1527,20211028,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1527","JDATE":"20211028","JTITLE":"竊盜"}